client.model

Interface IClientModel

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ClientModel

    public interface IClientModel
    The datastructure that represent the Client in a Catan Game Domain: TurnTracker, Winner (Player), version (>=0), chat, log, CatanMap, Players (0-4) bank, BonusTracker, TradeOffer, LocalPlayer, Deck.
    Precondition:
    The JSONObject must generated from the json from the server. Constructor: Can not be null and must contains all the fields as specified in the client model json spec.
    Postcondition:
    The ClientModel will be created according to the json returned by the server. The TurnTracker, Chat, Log, and Players will be build based on json.
